    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vaulting horses fitted with pommels, which are knob-like projections rising from the surface; may also be fitted with two graspable arch-like handles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
